channel.title: Weird items on map cant get them off? Delta
channel.description:
So i decided to go back to delta to try to gain more experience and have fun with rsps's like i used to and for some reason on every client/server i add theres these items that spawn on the ground on some fences and stuff and i have no idea how to resolve this problem. Does anyone know how to fix this? Heres a picture of how it looks.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/t2iy8cF.png[/img]
I already deleted all models in model folder to.

item.dc:creator: @hadlich4 hadlich4
item.description:
@hadlich4 wrote:

[quote=“Vain_, post:4, topic:525479”]the model was added to the cache and overwrote the fence model id.

you need to replace the cache with a fresh 317/377 cache[/quote]

Ok thanks man appreciate i’ll let you know what happens.
